        public byte[] getBytes()

      • getEncoded

        public byte[] getEncoded()
        Method getEncoded will return a CHUID object encoded by this class which will alter any previously encoded CHUID object. If the desire is to obtain the original CHUID bytes, consider using the getBytes() method.
